{"priority": "minor", "kind": "bug", "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}ts=1694483"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "gazebo", "full_name": "osrf/gazebo", "uuid": "{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}"}, "links": {"attachments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/673/attachments_page=1.json"}, "self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/673.json"}, "watch": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/673/watch"}, "comments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/673/comments_page=1.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/673/when-model-is-renamed-access-to-links"}, "vote": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/673/vote"}}, "reporter": {"display_name": "Brian Gerkey", "uuid": "{3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:2e35028e-9ad8-4d6a-a3a5-275159a304a9/5fa9ec73-0fec-4860-a202-e34ae23b6a12/128"}}, "nickname": "Brian Gerkey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:2e35028e-9ad8-4d6a-a3a5-275159a304a9"}, "title": "When model is renamed, access to links requires extra scope", "component": {"name": "physics", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/components/122876.json"}}}, "votes": 1, "watches": 6, "content": {"raw": "The `polaris_ranger_ev` model is brought into `vrc_task_1.world` with the name `drc_vehicle`.  To access links within that model requires nonintuitive extra scoping on the name, to include the model's original name, e.g.:\r\n\r\n    physics::ModelPtr vehicle = this->world->GetModel(\"drc_vehicle\");\r\n    physics::LinkPtr chassisLink = vehicle->GetLink(\"polaris_ranger_ev::chassis\");\r\n\r\nI would have expected that second line to be:\r\n\r\n    physics::LinkPtr chassisLink = vehicle->GetLink(\"chassis\");\r\n\r\nBut that doesn't work.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>The <code>polaris_ranger_ev</code> model is brought into <code>vrc_task_1.world</code> with the name <code>drc_vehicle</code>.  To access links within that model requires nonintuitive extra scoping on the name, to include the model's original name, e.g.:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"nt\">physics</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">ModelPtr</span> <span class=\"nt\">vehicle</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nt\">this-</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"nt\">world-</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"nt\">GetModel</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;drc_vehicle&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">);</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">physics</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">LinkPtr</span> <span class=\"nt\">chassisLink</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nt\">vehicle-</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"nt\">GetLink</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;polaris_ranger_ev::chassis&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">);</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>I would have expected that second line to be:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"nt\">physics</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">LinkPtr</span> <span class=\"nt\">chassisLink</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nt\">vehicle-</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"nt\">GetLink</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;chassis&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">);</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>But that doesn't work.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "new", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2013-05-03T02:00:10.686411+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2017-01-06T19:43:34.070555+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 673}